38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 12=

40
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,750
Is there anything else?

41
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,600
If not, let's call it a day.

42
00:02:41,610 --> 00:02:43,550
I have bandits to kill
in the mountains tomorrow.

43
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,740
(No. 2, No. 3)
No, 3,

44
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,190
we've been here for so long.

45
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,640
May I know

46
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,960
your name?

47
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:51,800
I go

48
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,310
by this name only.

49
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,640
It's

50
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:56,190
Chen Jinnan!

51
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:01,260
(Realm Sect: Core Members, Mirror Holders)

52
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,110
Did you draw this table?

53
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,270
Yes.

54
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:07,200
It looks creative.

55
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:10,800
Tell me about it.

56
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,320
As you can see,

57
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,990
the Realm Sect holds nine core members.

58
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:18,200
They're holders of the Jade Mirrors, too,

59
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:20,430
and sorted by their mirror numbers.

60
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,430
No. 1 is in the capital

61
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,360
with powerful figures behind, I believe.

62
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,710
He's likely to work for the court.

63
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,390
No. 6 seems

64
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,920
straightforward

65
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:31,080
and easygoing.

66
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:33,390
We can use him to our advantage.

67
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,710
As for No. 3,

68
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,040
he's charming,

69
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,870
fun to hang out with,

70
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:38,800
faithful,

71
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,830
and upright.

72
00:03:39,830 --> 00:03:41,760
Identity: Copper Gong Guardian.

73
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,920
Yes, that's me.

74
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:50,430
As for No. 5, No. 7, No. 8,

75
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:51,670
we haven't talked.

76
00:03:51,670 --> 00:03:52,920
It's hard to say.

77
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:55,080
No. 2, Li Miaozhen,

78
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:56,520
is in Yunzhou,

79
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,710
devoted to killing bandits.

80
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,670
People call her Winged Woman.

81
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:01,760
No. 4, Chu Yuanzhen, is

82
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,550
the Chief Disciple of the Treasure Sect.

83
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,640
Those two have been hostile

84
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,320
to each other for a long time.

85
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:12,320
He's also

86
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,390
the Saint of Men.

87
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,520
Do you know him, Lord Wei?

88
00:04:17,990 --> 00:04:20,640
Li Miaozhen must be the Saintess of Heaven.

89
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,320
Heaven and Men

90
00:04:22,670 --> 00:04:23,870
have never ceased fighting.

91
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,640
Those two will battle someday.

92
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:32,390
Have you found out why Jinlian

93
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,320
founded the Realm Sect?

94
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,550
He said after the Head

95
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,920
of Earth was demonized,

96
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:42,080
he founded the Realm Sect.

97
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,040
He gave the Jade Mirrors

98
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,390
to the best talents all over the world

99
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,800
and supported them

100
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,270
to gain their help

101
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,390
when he cleaned house.

102
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:55,080
The Earth Sect is traceless.

103
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:57,920
The Guardians still don't know everything

104
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,240
about the Sect Head's demonetization.

105
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:03,360
He knew you were a Guardian

106
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,640
but didn't hide anything.

107
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,320
Do you know why?

108
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,080
Are you saying

109
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,790
he meant to form an alliance

110
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:17,320
with you secretly through me?

111
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,280
You'll

112
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:23,350
be the Guardians' spy in the Realm Sect

113
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,150
to watch the Earth Sect's every move.

114
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,000
Our office

115
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:30,440
will assist you if necessary.

116
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,720
Yes.

117
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,080
Have you reached the Qi Stage?

118
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:37,790
You may begin

119
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,710
learning supreme skills.

120
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:43,030
Li Yuchun'll help you select a manual
from the Sutra Library.

121
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:45,680
Do you use a saber or a sword?

122
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:46,800
Both are fine.

123
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,230
Saber.

124
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,320
Choose a saber manual

125
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,680
that's simple and plain.

126
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:56,440
Ignore the flashy and fancy ones.

127
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:57,760
Keep in mind.

128
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,470
Fighters,

129
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,910
unlike other cultivators,

130
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,830
barely have any super power.

131
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:05,150
They rely on strength.

132
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,160
That's why

133
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:09,080
the simplest is the best.

134
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:13,760
When you reach even higher stages,

135
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,350
you'll know better.

136
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,030
Thanks for your teaching.

137
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:29,540
(Sutra Library, Supreme Saber Manual Archive)

138
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,520
You're good.

139
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,880
You went to the Haoqi Tower again.

140
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,790
Lord Wei summoned me.

141
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,470
I couldn't say no to him, Chief.

142
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:44,080
This way, please.

143
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:45,350
No, I'll show him.

144
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:55,470
The Manual Archive keeps 407 saber manuals.

145
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:58,320
They're all here.

146
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,470
Are you wondering

147
00:07:07,270 --> 00:07:09,560
which one is the strongest?

148
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,910
Supreme skills are divided

149
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,390
into techniques

150
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:16,790
and paths.

151
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:20,000
The latter is out of your league.

152
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,440
There are

153
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,200
no strong or weak skills.

154
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,200
They depend on you.

155
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,960
This is the saber manual I use.

156
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,860
Would you like to take a look?

157
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:35,100
(72 Dazzling Skills)
72 Skills?

158
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,150
Choose a saber manual

159
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,590
that's simple and plain.

160
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,760
Ignore the flashy and fancy ones.

161
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,230
Chief,

162
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,320
this saber manual

163
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,790
is too good.

164
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,270
I'm afraid

165
00:07:53,590 --> 00:07:54,830
I can't handle it.

166
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,520
Not just you.

167
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,960
Even I haven't

168
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:02,000
mastered everything in it.

169
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:06,440
Look around and choose carefully.

170
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,720
Yes!

171
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:11,230
"Fiery Clouds".

172
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,440
There really is such a manual.

173
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,470
"Nine-Dragon Whips"!

174
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:17,560
Did Nangong Qianrou learn from this manual?

175
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:22,150
"136 Chops on Mount Huashan".

176
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:24,880
Why chop it so many times?

177
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,000
Are you torn?

178
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,760
Are there new supreme skill manuals?

179
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,230
Saber manuals.

180
00:08:36,230 --> 00:08:38,320
The Bureau sent one over a few days ago

181
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,230
and said it'd require a weapon

182
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,560
to unleash the power.

183
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,270
Otherwise, it'd be useless.

184
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,910
A weapon?

185
00:08:45,710 --> 00:08:48,880
That's only for those above the Gold Gongs.

186
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,790
Do you mind fetching it?

187
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,230
I'd like to take a look.

188
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,080
Sure.

189
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:55,140
(One Chop to Kill All)

190
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,960
One Chop?

191
00:09:01,830 --> 00:09:05,390
"Nothing in the world can survive this chop.

192
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,440
If there is,

193
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:08,000
my advice is

194
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:09,880
run."

195
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,760
Fighters

196
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,320
must not panic in battle.

197
00:09:14,710 --> 00:09:16,230
We can't run away!

198
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,270
"Chop once

199
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,910
with a clear conscience.

200
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:24,120
It can reshape the universe."

201
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,920
Can one really reshape the universe?

202
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,320
Impossible.

203
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:35,320
Even Duke Zhenbei

204
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,280
cannot reshape the universe.

205
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,040
This manual is

206
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,080
(One Chop to Kill All)
a game of bluff.

207
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,680
It's worthless.

208
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,400
It doesn't suit you.

209
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,750
Choose something else.

210
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,750
But I think

211
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:49,280
it's perfect.

212
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,440
Do you have a weapon?

213
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,000
No.

214
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,560
But I might get one in the future.

215
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,160
I can keep this manual for now.

216
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,440
This is your only chance.

217
00:10:00,990 --> 00:10:02,510
Think twice.

218
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,800
No need.

219
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,070
I'll take it.

220
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,060
(One Chop to Kill All)

221
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:10,320
One Chop to Kill All?

222
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,710
Yes.

223
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:12,680
I told him

224
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,440
it'd require a weapon.

225
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,350
Don't waste such a good chance.

226
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:18,350
But Copper Gong Xu took it anyway.

227
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,110
I see.

228
00:10:21,110 --> 00:10:22,110
You may leave.

229
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:26,430
What's wrong?

230
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,470
Anything else?

231
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,280
Hearing that he had to pay 300 liang for it,

232
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:32,590
he said he didn't bring that much,

233
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,510
and he'd pay later.

234
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,710
But given his tone,

235
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:36,040
I don't think he will.

236
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,470
Deduct it from his salary.

237
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,000
Yes.

238
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:46,110
The Bureau.

239
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,000
Master,

240
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,590
Lord Wei is wise.

241
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:50,990
After all that we've done,

242
00:10:50,990 --> 00:10:52,710
he must be alerted.

243
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:54,590
It's fine.

244
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,160
Anyway,

245
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,080
he'd find out sooner or later.

246
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,400
You found out, huh?

247
00:11:02,230 --> 00:11:04,590
It was your order, wasn't it?

248
00:11:04,590 --> 00:11:05,750
I knew

249
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:08,160
the manual came too easily.

250
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:11,470
When I visited the Bureau earlier,

251
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,230
I told Supervisor

252
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,040
to look after you covertly.

253
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,830
Although you've found out,

254
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,680
do keep a low profile.

255
00:11:20,470 --> 00:11:21,510
Do not tell others

256
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,590
about today's incident.

257
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:26,440
You aren't their member.

258
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,750
Such special treatment might ruin

259
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,320
Supervisor's name.

260
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,470
Today's incident?

261
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,590
What happened today?

262
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:37,640
I...

263
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,440
lost my memory.

264
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,710
I don't remember

265
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,120
what happened.

266
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,320
Clever!

267
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,080
You deserve a drink

268
00:11:58,470 --> 00:12:00,080
(Liquor)
for your cleverness.

269
00:12:00,470 --> 00:12:01,310
Sit.

270
00:12:05,830 --> 00:12:06,710
Sit with us, Gang.

271
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:07,550
Thanks.

272
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:09,780
(Liquor)

273
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:13,110
Princess Huaiqing, benevolent

274
00:12:13,110 --> 00:12:15,280
and kind masters like you are rare.

275
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:16,510
I'm so fortunate

276
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:18,110
to be able to serve you.

277
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:19,230
Alright.

278
00:12:19,230 --> 00:12:20,470
I'll make toasts.

279
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:22,200
A toast to you, Your Highness.

280
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,080
Thank you for cultivating me.

281
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,110
I'll drink up.

282
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,400
Next, I toast you, Gang.

283
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:34,200
You're above me in terms of seniority.

284
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,320
- Thanks.
- You're humble.

285
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,160
I'll drink up.

286
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:45,040
Do you mean

287
00:12:45,470 --> 00:12:47,160
you chose me because I appreciated you

288
00:12:47,590 --> 00:12:48,830
and treated you well?

