00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:26,120
Rescuing him under the Guardians' noses

578
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,120
is almost impossible.

579
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,640
Whoever makes the move,

580
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,840
they'll get into trouble.

581
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:32,820
(No. 4)

582
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,300
(1, 3, 4, 5, 6)

583
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,780
(No. 3, No. 6)

584
00:23:35,780 --> 00:23:37,820
(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6)

585
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,100
(No. 3)

586
00:23:40,710 --> 00:23:42,160
I never meant to

587
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,070
trouble all of you.

588
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:46,800
I will

589
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,550
take responsibility

590
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:50,680
for my actions.

591
00:23:51,740 --> 00:23:53,220
(No. 6)

592
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:56,630
No. 6,

593
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:57,980
where are you now?

594
00:23:57,980 --> 00:24:01,100
(No. 6)

595
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,310
You guys, go this way.

596
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:04,440
You two, that way!

597
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,300
You guys follow me!

598
00:24:15,550 --> 00:24:16,710
Check every corner.

599
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:18,990
Leave no stone unturned!

600
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:19,960
Yes.

601
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,960
"A scholar's robe

602
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,640
carrying the great spirit

603
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:17,360
can conceal murderous energy."

604
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,600
No. 3 is

605
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:21,710
from the Yunlu Academy!

606
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:27,070
(Buddhist Staff?)

607
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,440
(He's from Tianyu.)

608
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:47,780
(Jiang Lyuzhong, Guardian, 4th Rank Fighter)

609
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,720
It's odd.

610
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,030
The crimson light is gone.

611
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,630
Song Tingfeng of the Breeze Hall.

612
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,160
Zhu Guangxiao of the Breeze Hall.

613
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:57,750
Greetings, Gold Gong Jiang.

614
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,790
Did you find any traces of the killer?

615
00:26:02,840 --> 00:26:03,790
We searched the streets.

616
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:04,710
There's no sign of him.

617
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,880
I found nothing either.

618
00:26:07,710 --> 00:26:08,550
Officers,

619
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:10,600
was the crimson light here?

620
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:12,160
Are you questioning us?

621
00:26:12,710 --> 00:26:13,550
I wouldn't dare.

622
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,750
Did you search down there?

623
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,790
Uh... no.

624
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,760
No.

625
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,710
Are you people of the Breeze Hall

626
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:32,160
always so reckless?

627
00:26:42,470 --> 00:26:43,310
Mr. Jiang,

628
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:44,380
we found this.

629
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:48,960
Chief.

630
00:26:58,550 --> 00:26:59,390
Looks like

631
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:01,030
some kind of weapon.

632
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,360
Why was it in the ditch?

633
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,840
Did the killer leave it there?

634
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:14,960
Report it to the high-ups.

635
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,040
Yes.

636
00:27:17,230 --> 00:27:18,070
Hold on!

637
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,480
Mr. Xu.

638
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:23,310
It really is him.

639
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,630
Mr. Xu, you haven't

640
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,200
gone to the Bureau for a while.

641
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,680
Senior Song keeps bringing you up.

642
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,960
Yes, Mr. Xu.

643
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,920
Do come for tea when you're free.

644
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:33,470
We're eager to learn
more alchemy skills from you.

645
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:34,750
- Alchemy?
- Not today.

646
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:35,920
I'm on duty now.

647
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:37,840
Yes, sure.

648
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:43,200
Sir, that's my device.

649
00:27:43,990 --> 00:27:44,960
It's yours?

650
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:47,160
Who are you? Which hall are you in?

651
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:48,960
He's one of us of the Breeze Hall.

652
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,160
He's Xu Qi'an.

653
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:56,680
Sir, Lord Wei gave that to me.

654
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:58,510
May I have it back?

655
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:00,920
Why was it in the ditch?

656
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,710
I had the runs just now.

657
00:28:06,710 --> 00:28:07,960
Perhaps

658
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,990
when I relieved myself,

659
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,750
it slipped out.

660
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:20,550
If you don't believe me,

661
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,270
check with Lord Wei.

662
00:28:25,360 --> 00:28:27,160
You're something else.

663
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,000
Yes.

664
00:28:28,010 --> 00:28:28,920
Ignore him.

665
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:30,630
Officers,

666
00:28:31,230 --> 00:28:32,750
do you know that Guardian

667
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:33,920
in our office?

668
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:35,750
We know him,

669
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,160
but he might not know us.

670
00:28:39,790 --> 00:28:40,630
How come?

671
00:28:40,990 --> 00:28:42,360
You know Senior Song Qing, right?

672
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:43,640
Supervisor called him

673
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:45,880
a once-in-a-century genius in alchemy.

674
00:28:47,070 --> 00:28:48,990
But Senior Song keeps saying this lately.

675
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:50,200
Do you know what it is?

676
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:52,030
"Xu Ningyan

677
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:54,310
is indeed my master."

678
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,680
Go to the Breeze Hall tomorrow

679
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:02,230
and bring him to our hall.

680
00:29:03,230 --> 00:29:04,070
Yes.

681
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:06,640
Hey, Ningyan,

682
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:07,710
you were amazing.

683
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:09,990
You won for our hall.

684
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:11,200
Shut up.

685
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:12,470
They can still hear us.

686
00:29:12,940 --> 00:29:13,790
So what?

687
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:14,990
We're with Ningyan.

688
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:17,120
What can a mere Gold Gong do to us?

689
00:29:17,510 --> 00:29:18,360
Look at them just now.

690
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:20,920
"Alchemy!"

691
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,270
You're good.

692
00:29:22,470 --> 00:29:23,920
I'm scared. I'm off.

693
00:29:26,790 --> 00:29:28,030
- What's so funny?
- Chief.

694
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:30,070
Stop slacking off.

695
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:31,350
Go find the killer!

696
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,680
Yes, on it!

697
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,880
Stop laughing. Go!

698
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,960
No. 3,

699
00:29:49,470 --> 00:29:51,310
why did you send me to a chicken coop?

700
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:01,220
(South Gate)

701
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:06,550
Go.

702
00:30:09,300 --> 00:30:10,150
What's on the cart?

703
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,570
- Search it.
- Just some supplies.

704
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:13,730
We made them.

705
00:30:14,610 --> 00:30:15,450
They're fine.

706
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:21,060
(Zhang's Plain and Meat Buns)

707
00:30:21,070 --> 00:30:22,160
We looked all night

708
00:30:22,470 --> 00:30:23,310
but found nothing.

709
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,000
We caught two thieves, though.

710
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:26,640
Not bad.

711
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,990
We'll get at least five qian.

712
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:32,030
(How's No. 6 doing now?)

713
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,270
We'll go back to report it to Chief.

714
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:35,350
Ningyan,

715
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:36,230
will you join us?

716
00:30:37,120 --> 00:30:38,750
I'm needed elsewhere. Go without me.

717
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:39,680
See you this afternoon.

718
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:44,000
That man...

719
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,120
(No. 6!)

720
00:30:46,270 --> 00:30:47,110
What about him?

721
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,360
He's just a scholar, isn't he?

722
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,520
No.

723
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:51,790
He is not.

724
00:30:51,990 --> 00:30:53,070
The robe he's wearing

725
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:54,310
is someone else's.

726
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:55,600
It doesn't fit at all.

727
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,400
He's walking

728
00:30:57,750 --> 00:30:58,640
with weak steps

729
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:00,070
as if he's out of strength.

730
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:01,550
Besides,

731
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,270
he came from the Inner City.

732
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:06,550
Do you mean...?

733
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:13,800
That's right.

734
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:15,920
He must've gone to the...

735
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,960
Imperial Office of Music.

736
00:31:24,790 --> 00:31:25,960
I want to go there, too.

737
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:28,120
Shall we go there tonight?

738
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:31,160
I'm exhausted!

739
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,020
I want to have fun.

740
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,440
Come on. Go back to rest.

741
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:36,680
I won't be tired at all in front of girls.

742
00:31:37,020 --> 00:31:40,460
(Breeze Hall)

743
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:01,440
Look at the time, guys.

744
00:32:01,990 --> 00:32:02,830
Aren't you going to

745
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:03,990
report it to Chief?

746
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,270
Already done.

747
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:11,750
Why not keep searching for the killer?

748
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:15,200
No rush. We haven't received the order.

749
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:20,160
How strange.

750
00:32:21,310 --> 00:32:23,120
This is a high-profile case.

751
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,640
It's not strange at all.

752
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:27,600
Earl Pingyuan was a scum anyway.

753
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:29,400
Lord Wei must be glad

754
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,640
that pest is dead.

755
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:35,510
Is that what he's like?

756
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,470
Put that away if your peanuts are baked.

757
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:40,470
It's burning my behind.

758
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,840
We searched the area
around Earl Pingyuan's Mansion overnight.

759
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:48,200
There's no sign of the killer in the houses

760
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:50,070
or the inns in the Inner City.

761
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,470
Those in white of the Bureau

762
00:32:51,470 --> 00:32:53,710
didn't sense the murderous energy either.

763
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:54,880
I'm sorry.

764
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:55,800
Please

765
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:56,920
punish me, Lord Wei.

766
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,840
Look at you, Mr. Jiang.

767
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,960
You let the killer get away

768
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,880
even with the Bureau's help.

769
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:05,880
Do you know those ill-willed court officials

770
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,790
are waiting to laugh at our office?

771
00:33:07,990 --> 00:33:09,440
I'll send in more people to search

772
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:10,710
in a wider area.

773
00:33:10,710 --> 00:33:11,600
I promise to

774
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:12,600
catch the killer

775
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:13,960
before tomorrow.

776
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:14,800
Relax.

777
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,440
You worked all night.

778
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,030
You must be tired.

779
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,270
Go back and rest.

780
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,110
Yes.

781
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,550
Lord Wei,

782
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:36,030
did you give anyone weapons lately?

783
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,270
What's your point?

784
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:43,120
I have something else to report to you.

785
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,720
Father,

786
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:52,070
the Ministry of Justice is

787
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:53,790
looking for the killer, too, in secret.

788
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,070
I think they want to beat us to it

789
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,270
and accuse the Guardians of inability.

790
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:00,440
If we couldn't find anything,

791
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:02,310
what could those losers do?

792
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:05,470
Lord Wei,

793
00:34:05,470 --> 00:34:06,710
Copper Gong Xu is here.

794
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:20,880
I have important things to report.

795
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,200
Speak.

796
00:34:25,270 --> 00:34:26,110
Lord Wei,

797
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,070
it's sensitive.

798
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:29,470
Can we speak in private?

799
00:34:30,470 --> 00:34:31,310
What?

800
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,790
Are you, a mere Copper Gong,
asking us to leave?

801
00:34:37,990 --> 00:34:38,840
You may go.

802
00:34:44,120 --> 00:34:45,030
Go.

803
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,440
Come up here.

804
00:34:54,470 --> 00:34:55,310
Yes.

805
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,630
Is it about the Realm Sect?

806
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,030
It's about Earl Pingyuan.

807
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,920
The one who killed him

808
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:12,880
is No. 6 of the Realm Sect.

809
00:35:14,990 --> 00:35:15,840
The motive?

810
00:35:22,670 --> 00:35:24,030
Letting a killer go

811
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,840
is as guilty as murder!

812
00:35:26,240 --> 00:35:27,240
Are you insane?

813
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:29,400
I'm sorry.

814
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:32,360
I'm guilty beyond forgiveness.

815
00:35:32,550 --> 00:35:33,880
I struggled overnight but couldn't

816
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,840
live with a guilty conscience.

817
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,190
I have to tell you the truth.

818
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:38,440
However you'll punish me,

819
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:39,630
I'll accept it.

820
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:51,840
Earlier today,

821
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,840
when I chatted with others,

822
00:35:54,590 --> 00:35:55,590
I learned

823
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,760
that you were rebuked by His Majesty.

824
00:35:58,510 --> 00:36:00,470
Other court officials ganged up on you

825
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:01,720
to bring you down.

826
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,990
I owe you more than I can repay.

827
00:36:04,990 --> 00:36:06,030
- I...
- Enough.

828
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:08,400
You don't

829
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,720
owe me.

830
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,960
Get to the point.

831
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:20,510
Earl Pingyuan secretly supported traffickers

832
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,400
to sell people

833
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:23,590
to rake in money!

834
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:26,280
They sold children and women

835
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:28,720
to brothels and sweatshops.

836
00:36:28,990 --> 00:36:30,070
They became thieves

837
00:36:30,470 --> 00:36:32,800
and even lost their limbs
to satisfy others' fetishes.

838
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,470
Hearing such inhumanity,

839
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:38,190
I'd rather kill those animals myself.

840
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:46,920
Get up.

841
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:52,510
Yes.

842
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,320
Xu Qi'an,

843
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:02,030
how well do you know

844
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,630
the Realm Sect?

845
00:37:05,760 --> 00:37:07,440
How well do you know Jinlian

846
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:08,920
of the Earth Sect?

847
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,470
Investigation shows

848
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:18,920
the Earl did keep a group of traffickers.

849
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,110
But did No. 6

850
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:23,550
kill him for his junior fellow

851
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:25,840
without any hidden agenda?

852
00:37:27,630 --> 00:37:28,510
Maybe

853
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:31,440
the Earl was involved in other things, too.

854
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:33,720
Maybe

855
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:37,990
those traffickers did something else

856
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,240
that led to their doom.

857
00:37:41,990 --> 00:37:43,510
Did you consider

858
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:46,030
all those possibilities?

859
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:50,360
(He's teaching me.)

860
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,190
(He's helping me grow.)

861
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:54,240
I was reckless.

862
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:55,510
Never mind.

863
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:56,550
You stay

864
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,760
out of this case.

865
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:01,150
I'll assign it to others.

866
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:03,550
Keep your cover in the Realm Sect.

867
00:38:04,150 --> 00:38:05,110
Your priority

868
00:38:05,110 --> 00:38:06,280
is to check out

869
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,920
the identity of everyone there.

870
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,600
And...

871
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,280
Stay safe.

872
00:38:25,190 --> 00:38:26,670
I'll give it my all, sir.

873
00:38:31,180 --> 00:38:32,100
(Peace)

874
00:38:32,100 --> 00:38:33,240
That's absurd!

875
