That Cooper Gong overreached himself.

877
00:38:36,990 --> 00:38:38,670
Clearly, he has no respect for you.

878
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:45,320
I'm sowing discord. Say something.

879
00:38:52,150 --> 00:38:54,030
You know how good he is

880
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:56,590
and how much Lord Wei values him.

881
00:38:56,720 --> 00:38:57,990
What do you expect me to say?

882
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:01,440
He doesn't respect you at all.

883
00:39:01,630 --> 00:39:02,670
You know that, too, right?

884
00:39:04,470 --> 00:39:06,070
That doesn't change the fact

885
