that he serves under me.

886
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,190
Wait and see, Yang Yan.

887
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:14,030
This isn't over.

888
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:17,390
Good day.

889
00:39:25,820 --> 00:39:30,460
