902
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:14,660
(No. 4)

903
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:15,510
How are you?

904
00:40:15,630 --> 00:40:16,550
Are you safe?

905
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:18,110
(No. 6)
