906
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:19,800
but wouldn't dare ask.

907
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:22,140
Thanks for your concern.

908
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,590
I'm safe for now.

909
00:40:24,990 --> 00:40:26,370
(No. 6)
So

910
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,670
did No. 3 help you out?

911
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,240
Yes.

912
00:40:30,190 --> 00:40:31,320
Thanks to him,

913
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,400
I made it out.

914
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,660
(No. 3)

915
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:38,190
Where is No. 3?

916
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:39,470
Is he in trouble?

917
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:41,590
He's blessed by the heavens.

918
00:40:42,110 --> 00:40:43,070
I'm sure he's fine.

919
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:44,660
(No. 3)

920
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,030
- No. 3!
- No. 6.

921
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,240
I heard the news.

922
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:50,550
(No. 6, No. 4, No. 2)
My office got anonymous tips.

923
00:40:50,550 --> 00:40:51,760
They'll keep going after you.

924
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,630
Be prepared

925
00:40:52,630 --> 00:40:53,550
and stay alert.

926
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:55,800
Thanks for the heads-up.

927
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,320
No. 3 has helped No. 6 out

928
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:01,070
and infiltrated into the Guardians.

929
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:03,510
I knew he was capable.

930
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:05,630
No. 6, now that No. 3 is here,

931
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:07,840
can you tell us how you got out?

932
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:10,640
No. 3,

933
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,240
can I...

934
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,350
I say it?

935
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,320
Why not?

936
00:41:16,400 --> 00:41:17,760
I have nothing to hide.

937
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:18,760
Go ahead.

938
00:41:18,990 --> 00:41:19,830
Sure.

939
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,240
Here's the thing.

940
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:22,720
No. 3

941
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:24,590
gave me a scholar's robe

942
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,110
to conceal my murderous energy.

943
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:27,990
Yes.

944
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:30,800
But that wasn't enough.

945
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:34,470
Then I brought him to an inn that no one knew

946
00:41:34,470 --> 00:41:35,360
to hide.

947
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:37,670
Even so,

948
00:41:37,910 --> 00:41:39,610
