the Guardians were everywhere.

949
00:41:39,740 --> 00:41:41,350
How did you hide from them?

950
00:41:41,630 --> 00:41:43,190
He couldn't.

951
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:46,880
After a while, they found traces of him.

952
00:41:47,320 --> 00:41:48,800
Thanks to my Plan B,

953
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,880
he made a narrow escape.

954
00:41:50,990 --> 00:41:51,880
What did you do?

955
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:54,960
I put on the robe I had got

956
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:56,030
from No. 6

957
00:41:56,190 --> 00:41:57,360
and jumped out of the window,

958
00:41:57,470 --> 00:41:59,760
drawing the attention of the Guardians

959
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:01,070
and those of the Bureau to me.

960
00:42:01,470 --> 00:42:03,590
Then No. 6 spent the rest of the night

961
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:04,920
in the mirror safely.

962
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:06,420
(No. 6)

963
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,400
Am I right,

964
00:42:07,670 --> 00:42:08,840
No. 6?

965
00:42:13,670 --> 00:42:14,590
Yes,

966
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:15,990
I guess.

967
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:21,670
(Looks like No. 6 isn't too dumb.)

968
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:22,960
(He can be my friend.)

969
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:23,950
Nice!

970
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:26,240
Creating a distraction is smart.

971
00:42:26,240 --> 00:42:27,260
