994
00:43:15,630 --> 00:43:17,440
As No. 6's fellow,

995
00:43:17,630 --> 00:43:20,240
I shall protect him.

996
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:21,080
Worry not.

997
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,990
Even if I meet my doom,

998
00:43:23,190 --> 00:43:25,400
I'll die a worthy death!

